data.description: Don't miss out on the chance to see this amazing 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 1,801 square foot home in Hanford! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by beautiful tile flooring, high ceilings, and a spacious hallway. Each room is generously sized and features new laminate flooring. The living room offers an open space for entertaining family and friends, with large windows that flood the area with natural light. The kitchen boasts a massive granite island, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom is both spacious and welcoming, with a master bath that includes dual sinks, a wide mirror, and even space for a vanity or bath. The walk-in closet is absolutely huge! Finally, the backyard features a covered patio with plenty of space to enjoy the outdoors. Don't wait - schedule your showing today!
